The laboratory, which was built within 14 days and capable of conducting tens of thousands of RT-PCR tests per day, was the world ' s first laboratory of this size to operate outside China.
China, France, Germany, Hong Kong, China, Japan and the United States have developed different detection methods for various parts of the coronary virus gene map.
