However, as a matter of caution, we hired anti-viral cleaners to completely disinfect the San Francisco office.
Using hospital-level disinfection solutions, they disinfect the surfaces and the halls and elevators leading to our floors.
Office buildings are fulfilling their duty-of-care agreements, using corresponding products to ensure the security of tenants.
We are confident that when you decide to return to work, the Office is well prepared to welcome you.
