Preventive measures to reduce the likelihood of infection include: staying at home; avoiding access to crowd-intensive areas; regularly washing hands with soap and water for at least 20 seconds; maintaining good respiratory hygiene; and avoiding touching eyes, nose or mouth without washing hands.
